---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';

const courseType = 'short online course';
const courseObjectives = 'provide foundational knowledge about voice-over work';
const subjectOrTopic = 'Voice-over';
const courseOutcomeOrGoal = 'performing automated voice-over work';
const professionOrAcademic = 'content creator'

const transcript = `
Good day everyone and welcome to ${SITE_TITLE}!

This comprehensive and engaging ${courseType} is designed to ${courseObjectives}. 

This course is tailored to provide you with a deep understanding of ${subjectOrTopic}, equipping you with the knowledge and skills necessary for ${courseOutcomeOrGoal}. 

Whether you're a beginner looking to explore a new field or an experienced ${professionOrAcademic}, this course will challenge and inspire you to achieve your professional goals.

The course covers
Understanding Voice-Over Basics
Introduction to the fundamentals of voice-over work, including its purpose and applications.
Exploring Voice Varieties
Get familiar with different voice styles, tones, and pitches commonly used in voice-over work.
Script Interpretation
How to analyze and interpret voice-over scripts, including understanding the target audience and the intended message.
Characterization
Explore techniques for creating different characters, personas, and voices.
Industry Awareness
Provide insights into the voice-over industry, including opportunities, trends, and career paths.
Legal and Ethical Considerations
Discuss legal and ethical considerations related to voice-over work, including contracts, royalties, and copyright issues.
Professionalism and Work Etiquette:
Emphasize professionalism, punctuality, and communication skills when working with clients and studios.
Feedback and Self-Improvement:
Give and receive constructive feedback on your voice-over performances.
Promote continuous self-improvement and practice.

Project Work:
Practical voice-over projects, including commercials, narrations, and character performances.
Portfolio Development:
Create a portfolio showcasing your best voice-over work to share with potential clients or employers.


Have fun! If you get stuck, we will be happy to help at Storyshell.io
`;

